/frankbrunolaw.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/NYC-Nursing-Home-Abuse-Lawyer1-300x179.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/frankbrunolaw.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/NYC-Nursing-Home-Abuse-Lawyer1-768x459.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f643f9d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f643f9d\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8617fae elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"8617fae\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Top Rated NYC Nursing Home Abuse Lawyer Representing Clients In Queens, Nassau, Brooklyn, and Throughout NY<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The decision to put our loved ones in a nursing home is never easy. However, we trust that the professionals at these facilities will provide our loved ones with the care that we are unable to provide our loved ones. Therefore, it can be devastating to discover that our loved ones have been the victim of abuse by the very people we trusted to protect them. An experienced nursing home abuse lawyer in NYC from the <a href=\"https:\/\/frankbrunolaw.com\/\">Law Offices of Bruno Reyes<\/a>, Jr. will help you hold those responsible for the abuse accountable for their actions.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>At the Law Offices of Bruno Reyes, we are committed to fighting on behalf of the vulnerable. We know how difficult it can be to deal with the fact that your loved one has been the victim of abuse. You may not even know what to do next. Our team is here for you. We will provide you with the guidance and support you need to get through this difficult time.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>Our team provides <a href=\"https:\/\/frankbrunolaw.com\/contact\/\">free initial consultation<\/a> for families of victims of nursing home abuse. We will review your case to determine your options and rights. We will investigate your case to uncover the truth. We will work to build a strong case in defense of your loved one. We have a long history of securing substantial settlements and verdicts. You can rely on us to work for the best outcome on your behalf.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #3ab3c7\"><a style=\"color: #3ab3c7\" href=\"https:\/\/frankbrunolaw.com\/contact\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Contact us today<\/a><\/span><\/strong>\u00a0to schedule your free consultation with an attorney from our law firm.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83c3c3e elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"83c3c3e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">What is Nursing Home Abuse?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Nursing home abuse is more common than many people would like to believe. Over 5 million elders in nursing homes suffer abuse annually. Over 44 percent of residents in nursing homes have reported suffering abuse while 90 percent have reported being neglected.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>There are different forms of abuse. These include:\u00a0<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a7834d elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"6a7834d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h3 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Physical abuse<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This is the form of abuse that many people associate with the term \u2018nursing home abuse.\u2019 It involves the intentional infliction of physical injury to the nursing home resident. This may include hitting or physically restraining the resident for no medical reason.\u00a0<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fd96048 elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"fd96048\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h3 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Neglect<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Neglect may not seem as serious as physical abuse but it is still a form of abuse and can have consequences that are just as serious as physical abuse. Neglect occurs when the nursing home staff fails to meet the needs of the nursing home resident. This may include not providing adequate or nutritious meals, not providing assistance to those with mobility issues and thus resulting in bed sores and other complications, or even failing to assist residents with their personal hygiene.\u00a0<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24546bf elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"24546bf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h3 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Sexual abuse<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Nursing home residents are often vulnerable. They are easy prey to sexual abuse from nursing home staff members. Sexual abuse may be physical or emotional. It may involve inappropriate touching, forced sexual intercourse, or even being forced to watch pornographic material.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a25586f elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"a25586f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Reach Out to the Law Offices of Bruno Reyes to Consult with an Experienced NYC Nursing Home Abuse Lawyer from Our Law Firm<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Do you suspect that a loved one has been the victim of nursing home abuse? The attorneys at the Law Offices of Bruno Reyes are experienced. You can trust us to provide you with the guidance you need during this difficult time.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>Don\u2019t hesitate to get in touch with us to <a href=\"https:\/\/frankbrunolaw.com\/contact\/\">schedule an appointment for a consultation<\/a> with an experienced NYC nursing home abuse lawyer. Our attorneys offer a free initial consultation for victims of nursing home abuse as well as their families. We will review your case and offer advice on the best approach to take.\u00a0<strong><span style=\"color: #3ab3c7\"><a style=\"color: #3ab3c7\" href=\"https:\/\/frankbrunolaw.com\/contact\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Contact us now<\/a><\/span><\/strong>\u00a0to learn what we can do for you.\u00a0<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b04f37 elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"8b04f37\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h3 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Emotional or psychological abuse<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Nursing home abuse may also be emotional or psychological. Staff members may intimidate, mock or even humiliate residents.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>No matter what form of abuse your loved one has suffered, you can rely on an experienced NYC nursing home abuse lawyer from the Law Offices of Bruno Reyes to defend your loved one\u2019s rights and seek justice on their behalf.\u00a0<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59e34d6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"59e34d6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-965f514 elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"965f514\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Frequently Asked Questions about Nursing Home Abuse in New York<\/h2><\/div><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f92d1a6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f92d1a6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ebb5670 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ebb5670\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2eb9a67 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"2eb9a67\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" role=\"button\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Question<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3be5e1f elementor-widget elementor-widget-hea